file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: PayloadV
  version: 0.0.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}/payloadV"
    variables:
      server:
        default: http://localhost
      port:
        default: "9090"
paths:
  /reservation:
    post:
      summary: Represents Snowpeak reservation resource
      operationId: postReservation
      requestBody:
        description: Reservation representation
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Link'
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Accepted
components:
  schemas:
    Salary:
      nullable: true
      oneOf:
        - type: integer
          format: int64
        - type: number
          format: float
        - type: number
          format: double
    Action:
      type: string
      nullable: true
    Count:
      type: number
      format: double
      nullable: true
    Rels:
      type: array
      nullable: true
      items:
        type: string
    Books:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        type: string
      nullable: true
    Link:
      required:
        - actions
        - books
        - rels
        - salary
      type: object
      properties:
        rels:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Rels'
        actions:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Action'
        count:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Count'
        books:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Books'
        salary:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Salary'
